    <rigor-reason>Audit + design task; no source modification; planning artifact only. STANDARD per task-execute Step 0.5 ("phase 2.x or higher, design doc output").</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <dependencies>none (Wave 5 + Wave 8 already complete; this task only reads code)</dependencies>
